Nollywood actress and filmmaker, Shan George, has responded to critics based on a comment she made about divorce. The actress took to her Instagram story on Monday to give her opinion on divorce and remarriage. She wrote, “One minute they are saying ‘Abeg if a marriage is not working, leave. Same people will still curse on d next person a man/woman who decides to date/marry after leaving the marriage that is not working. Shay if one leaves a shitty marriage, make e no marry again or what?”(sic) Gospel Singer, Sammie Okposo, Publicly Apologises For Cheating On His Wife Juwon Is My Son 100%, Mercy Aigbe’s Ex- Husband Confirms Paternity However, her opinion didn’t sit down well with some of her fans as some of them accused her of encouraging divorce and others wondered why she is supporting fellow actress, Mercy Aigbe, for her recent revelation. George took to her Instagram story again to respond to these critics. She said, “motherfuckers so quick to say I’m disappointed in u yen yen yen!!! Wen you were not disappointed, how much did you send me?”